  Locus:
    Page: 472
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Thoughts
---
When I want to think things more pleasant, I close the cupboards of my mind
revealing the more unpleasant things of life, and open the cupboards
containing the more pleasant thoughts. If I want to sleep, I close up all
the cupboards of my mind.
